üß† Key Learnings
	‚Ä¢	IoT & Cloud: Reliable real-time sensor communication is achievable at scale using AWS IoT Core
	‚Ä¢	Digital Twin Modeling: Accurate virtual systems require deep domain knowledge of plants/fish
	‚Ä¢	Resource Optimization: Data-driven decisions improved efficiency (water, nutrients) dramatically
	‚Ä¢	Scalable Research: Lessons from single plant monitoring scaled to complex ecosystems
	‚Ä¢	Edge Computing Matters: Processing on Raspberry Pi reduced cloud bandwidth by 40%
	‚Ä¢	Visualization & Alerts: Grafana dashboards enable instant insights and preventive action


